Tell a friend At Google, we believe that a diverse mix of voices leads to better discussions, decisions, and outcomes for everyone. If you’re considering attending GDD India, but running into roadblocks, email us at gdd-india@google.com and we’ll see how we can help. We all grow from sharing our diverse expertise and experiences. Help us ensure a diversity of perspectives at GDD India by extending invitations to diverse colleagues or industry professionals.Your ticket is non-transferable. If you can no longer attend the event, we kindly ask you to cancel your registration by emailing gdd-india@google.com. This will open up a spot for others on the waitlist.
